FlashBank — for agents
======================
MCP: npx -y @flashbank/mcp   (zero-config, read-only)
Agent guide (prose): https://flashbank.net/llms.txt

Read the flash-loan and P2P markets over MCP, then act through the apps under
Links. Read access needs no key. There is no in-client (gopher) action yet —
the markets are driven through the MCP server and the web apps.
